&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;LED&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Control LED by using pin 13 (Same as Arduino UNO)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;sample-app&#34;&gt;Sample App&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.leafony.com/en/docs/examples/beginner/1_p/basic/blink&#34;&gt;Blink&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-to-use-it-with-arduino&#34;&gt;How to use it with Arduino&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In order to use this leaf with Arduino, the board must be configured on the Arduino IDE.&lt;br&gt;
Please refer to &lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.leafony.com/en/docs/environment/avr/arduino&#34;&gt;Environment&lt;/a&gt;  for instructions.&lt;/p&gt;
