&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Leafony/HW-Design-Files/blob/master/AP01_AVR_MCU/AP01_AVR_MCU_Schematic.pdf&#34;&gt;Schematic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Leafony/HW-Design-Files/blob/master/AP01_AVR_MCU/AP01_AVR_MCU_ComponentMarking.pdf&#34;&gt;Component marking&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
