&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/arduino/ArduinoCore-avr/blob/master/bootloaders/atmega/ATmegaBOOT_168_atmega328_pro_8MHz.hex&#34;&gt;Bootloader&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
